\sum_{\pm} \frac{1}{|T'|\circ T_\pm^{-1}} = \sum_{\pm} \frac{x_\pm^2}{1+ x_\pm^2} = \frac{x_-^2+2 (x_- x_+)^2+x_+^2}{1+ x_-^2 + x_+^2 + (x_- x_+)^2}  = \frac{2+x_-^2+x_+^2}{2+ x_-^2 + x_+^2} = 1.
